 er.. d00d.  This is the Blast Furnace.  NOBODY has an &quot;established network of friends&quot; here.  In game, yea.  On here, <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>EVERYONE</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> is, has been, and always will be fair game when they make any sort of post or comment here, whether it's a stupid one or not.<br>
