 <br>
 This isn't a children's playroom, nor is it a circle jerk.  Nobody is snuggling up to anyone else here.<br>
<br>
The problem here is that in <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>YOUR</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> mind you have decided that's how it is. The human mind is a scary thing if it's misused.  You can convince yourself of things that have no basis in reality, and it becomes real to you.  Psychologists know this. It's not an opinion, it's a documented fact.  I would suggest reading up on it.. maybe speaking to a professional about it. You might discover something about yourself that you didn't know.<br>
<br>
 Everyone else reading and posting in this place seems to know the score, and realize they are a target just by being here.  The more you post, the more you become the target. Especially if you post conspiracy theories about everyone ganging up on you<br>
.  EVERYONE jumps on that one, and it's not true until that point. All of a sudden you MAKE it true by making yourself the most desirable target.  Not because anyone decided to help each other, but because you drew their attention.<br>
